{
  "video_id": "7sqeoYOQ4qg",
  "title": "How to fix a broken education system ... without any more money | Seema Bansal",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12759.0,
      "end_time": 15109.0,
      "text": "So we all have our own biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15133.0,
      "end_time": 17784.0,
      "text": "For example, some of us tend to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17808.0,
      "end_time": 21417.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s very difficult to transform failing government systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21871.0,
      "end_time": 23618.0,
      "text": "When we think of government systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23642.0,
      "end_time": 27233.0,
      "text": "we tend to think that they&#39;re archaic, set in their ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27257.0,
      "end_time": 29953.0,
      "text": "and perhaps, the leadership is just too bureaucratic"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29977.0,
      "end_time": 31382.0,
      "text": "to be able to change things."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32970.0,
      "end_time": 35112.0,
      "text": "Well, today, I want to challenge that theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35886.0,
      "end_time": 39955.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you a story of a very large government system"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39979.0,
      "end_time": 43423.0,
      "text": "that has not only put itself on the path of reform"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43447.0,
      "end_time": 46636.0,
      "text": "but has also shown fairly spectacular results"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46660.0,
      "end_time": 47995.0,
      "text": "in less than three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48746.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "This is what a classroom in a public school in India looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53500.0,
      "end_time": 55401.0,
      "text": "There are 1 million such schools in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55878.0,
      "end_time": 59100.0,
      "text": "And even for me, who&#39;s lived in India all her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59340.0,
      "end_time": 62800.0,
      "text": "walking into one of these schools is fairly heartbreaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63106.0,
      "end_time": 65175.0,
      "text": "By the time kids are 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65199.0,
      "end_time": 69231.0,
      "text": "50 percent of them have fallen so far behind in their education"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69255.0,
      "end_time": 70994.0,
      "text": "that they have no hope to recover."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71606.0,
      "end_time": 74404.0,
      "text": "11-year-olds cannot do simple addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74428.0,
      "end_time": 77310.0,
      "text": "they cannot construct a grammatically correct sentence."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77779.0,
      "end_time": 81420.0,
      "text": "These are things that you and I would expect an 8-year-old"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81660.0,
      "end_time": 82334.0,
      "text": "to be able to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82672.0,
      "end_time": 85469.0,
      "text": "By the time kids are 13 or 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85493.0,
      "end_time": 87273.0,
      "text": "they tend to drop out of schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88313.0,
      "end_time": 91587.0,
      "text": "In India, public schools not only offer free education --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91611.0,
      "end_time": 95240.0,
      "text": "they offer free textbooks, free workbooks, free meals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95480.0,
      "end_time": 97118.0,
      "text": "sometimes even cash scholarships."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97691.0,
      "end_time": 100676.0,
      "text": "And yet, 40 percent of the parents today"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100700.0,
      "end_time": 103880.0,
      "text": "are choosing to pull their children out of public schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103904.0,
      "end_time": 107420.0,
      "text": "and pay out of their pockets to put them in private schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107445.0,
      "end_time": 111110.0,
      "text": "As a comparison, in a far richer country, the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111134.0,
      "end_time": 113550.0,
      "text": "that number is only 10 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113377.0,
      "end_time": 118330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a huge statement on how broken the Indian public education system is."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119431.0,
      "end_time": 123907.0,
      "text": "So it was with that background that I got a call in the summer of 2013"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123931.0,
      "end_time": 127753.0,
      "text": "from an absolutely brilliant lady called Surina Rajan."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127778.0,
      "end_time": 131895.0,
      "text": "She was, at that time, the head of the Department of School Education"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131919.0,
      "end_time": 134185.0,
      "text": "in a state called Haryana in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 134209.0,
      "end_time": 137280.0,
      "text": "So she said to us, \"Look, I&#39;ve been heading this department"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137304.0,
      "end_time": 138530.0,
      "text": "for the last two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138554.0,
      "end_time": 141985.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve tried a number of things, and nothing seems to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142800.0,
      "end_time": 143470.0,
      "text": "Can you possibly help?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144852.0,
      "end_time": 147666.0,
      "text": "Let me describe Haryana a little bit to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147690.0,
      "end_time": 151490.0,
      "text": "Haryana is a state which has 30 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151721.0,
      "end_time": 154892.0,
      "text": "It has 15,000 public schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154916.0,
      "end_time": 157751.0,
      "text": "and 2 million plus children in those public schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158119.0,
      "end_time": 160563.0,
      "text": "So basically, with that phone call,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160587.0,
      "end_time": 163900.0,
      "text": "I promised to help a state and system"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163330.0,
      "end_time": 167356.0,
      "text": "which was as large as that of Peru or Canada transform itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168591.0,
      "end_time": 172168.0,
      "text": "As I started this project, I was very painfully aware of two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172192.0,
      "end_time": 175403.0,
      "text": "One, that I had never done anything like this before."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175427.0,
      "end_time": 179802.0,
      "text": "And two, many others had, perhaps without too much success."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180247.0,
      "end_time": 183900.0,
      "text": "As my colleagues and I looked across the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183330.0,
      "end_time": 184340.0,
      "text": "and across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184365.0,
      "end_time": 186233.0,
      "text": "we couldn&#39;t find another example"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186257.0,
      "end_time": 189830.0,
      "text": "that we could just pick up and replicate in Haryana."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189107.0,
      "end_time": 191607.0,
      "text": "We knew that we had to craft our own journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192692.0,
      "end_time": 195746.0,
      "text": "But anyway, we jumped right in and as we jumped in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195770.0,
      "end_time": 198509.0,
      "text": "all sorts of ideas started flying at us."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198533.0,
      "end_time": 201571.0,
      "text": "People said, \"Let&#39;s change the way we recruit teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201595.0,
      "end_time": 204339.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s hire new principals and train them"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204363.0,
      "end_time": 206581.0,
      "text": "and send them on international learning tours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206605.0,
      "end_time": 209103.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s put technology inside classrooms.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209128.0,
      "end_time": 211733.0,
      "text": "By the end of week one, we had 50 ideas on the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211758.0,
      "end_time": 213986.0,
      "text": "all amazing, all sounded right."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214100.0,
      "end_time": 218713.0,
      "text": "There was no way we were going to be able to implement 50 things."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219103.0,
      "end_time": 220853.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"Hang on, stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221175.0,
      "end_time": 224424.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s first at least decide what is it we&#39;re trying to achieve.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224448.0,
      "end_time": 227222.0,
      "text": "So with a lot of push and pull and debate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227246.0,
      "end_time": 231133.0,
      "text": "Haryana set itself a goal which said: by 2020,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231157.0,
      "end_time": 235144.0,
      "text": "we want 80 percent of our children to be at grade-level knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235590.0,
      "end_time": 238473.0,
      "text": "Now the specifics of the goal don&#39;t matter here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238497.0,
      "end_time": 241411.0,
      "text": "but what matters is how specific the goal is."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241786.0,
      "end_time": 244758.0,
      "text": "Because it really allowed us to take all those ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244782.0,
      "end_time": 246207.0,
      "text": "which were being thrown at us"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246231.0,
      "end_time": 248605.0,
      "text": "and say which ones we were going to implement."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248629.0,
      "end_time": 252947.0,
      "text": "Does this idea support this goal? If yes, let&#39;s keep it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252972.0,
      "end_time": 256252.0,
      "text": "But if it doesn&#39;t or we&#39;re not sure, then let&#39;s put it aside."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256276.0,
      "end_time": 260900.0,
      "text": "As simple as it sounds, having a very specific goal right up front"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260923.0,
      "end_time": 264140.0,
      "text": "has really allowed us to be very sharp and focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 264164.0,
      "end_time": 265792.0,
      "text": "in our transformation journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265816.0,
      "end_time": 268433.0,
      "text": "And looking back over the last two and a half years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268458.0,
      "end_time": 270420.0,
      "text": "that has been a huge positive for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271488.0,
      "end_time": 272652.0,
      "text": "So we had the goal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272676.0,
      "end_time": 276820.0,
      "text": "and now we needed to figure out what are the issues, what is broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 277100.0,
      "end_time": 279727.0,
      "text": "Before we went into schools, a lot of people told us"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279752.0,
      "end_time": 281818.0,
      "text": "that education quality is poor"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281842.0,
      "end_time": 285716.0,
      "text": "because either the teachers are lazy, they don&#39;t come into schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 285740.0,
      "end_time": 288974.0,
      "text": "or they&#39;re incapable, they actually don&#39;t know how to teach."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 289427.0,
      "end_time": 293710.0,
      "text": "Well, when we went inside schools, we found something completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 293734.0,
      "end_time": 297317.0,
      "text": "On most days, most teachers were actually inside schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297771.0,
      "end_time": 299350.0,
      "text": "And when you spoke with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299374.0,
      "end_time": 303185.0,
      "text": "you realized they were perfectly capable of teaching elementary classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303952.0,
      "end_time": 305756.0,
      "text": "But they were not teaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306702.0,
      "end_time": 308101.0,
      "text": "I went to a school"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308125.0,
      "end_time": 311209.0,
      "text": "where the teachers were getting the construction of a classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311233.0,
      "end_time": 313311.0,
      "text": "and a toilet supervised."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313645.0,
      "end_time": 315287.0,
      "text": "I went to another school"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315311.0,
      "end_time": 318202.0,
      "text": "where two of the teachers had gone to a nearby bank branch"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318226.0,
      "end_time": 320968.0,
      "text": "to deposit scholarship money into kids&#39; accounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 321452.0,
      "end_time": 325743.0,
      "text": "At lunchtime, most teachers were spending all of their time"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325767.0,
      "end_time": 329868.0,
      "text": "getting the midday meal cooking, supervised and served to the students."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 330907.0,
      "end_time": 332111.0,
      "text": "So we asked the teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 332135.0,
      "end_time": 334883.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s going on, why are you not teaching?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335196.0,
      "end_time": 337383.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"This is what&#39;s expected of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338500.0,
      "end_time": 340811.0,
      "text": "When a supervisor comes to visit us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340835.0,
      "end_time": 343224.0,
      "text": "these are exactly the things that he checks."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 343248.0,
      "end_time": 345928.0,
      "text": "Has the toilet been made, has the meal been served."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345952.0,
      "end_time": 349620.0,
      "text": "When my principal goes to a meeting at headquarters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 349860.0,
      "end_time": 351473.0,
      "text": "these are exactly the things which are discussed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352481.0,
      "end_time": 356505.0,
      "text": "You see, what had happened was, over the last two decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 356529.0,
      "end_time": 360359.0,
      "text": "India had been fighting the challenge of access, having enough schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360383.0,
      "end_time": 363154.0,
      "text": "and enrollment, bringing children into the schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 363178.0,
      "end_time": 366608.0,
      "text": "So the government launched a whole host of programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 366632.0,
      "end_time": 368491.0,
      "text": "to address these challenges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 368515.0,
      "end_time": 373272.0,
      "text": "and the teachers became the implicit executors of these programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 373296.0,
      "end_time": 375444.0,
      "text": "Not explicitly, but implicitly."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376652.0,
      "end_time": 381668.0,
      "text": "And now, what was actually needed was not to actually train teachers further"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 381692.0,
      "end_time": 383591.0,
      "text": "or to monitor their attendance"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 383615.0,
      "end_time": 387486.0,
      "text": "but to tell them that what is most important"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 387510.0,
      "end_time": 390110.0,
      "text": "is for them to go back inside classrooms and teach."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 390134.0,
      "end_time": 393988.0,
      "text": "They needed to be monitored and measured and awarded"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 394120.0,
      "end_time": 395360.0,
      "text": "on the quality of teaching"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 395384.0,
      "end_time": 397227.0,
      "text": "and not on all sorts of other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 398180.0,
      "end_time": 400477.0,
      "text": "So as we went through the education system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 400502.0,
      "end_time": 405762.0,
      "text": "as we delved into it deeper, we found a few such core root causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 405786.0,
      "end_time": 409918.0,
      "text": "which were determining, which were shaping how people behaved in the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 409942.0,
      "end_time": 413625.0,
      "text": "And we realized that unless we change those specific things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 413649.0,
      "end_time": 415602.0,
      "text": "we could do a number of other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 415626.0,
      "end_time": 418469.0,
      "text": "We could train, we could put technology into schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 418493.0,
      "end_time": 420473.0,
      "text": "but the system wouldn&#39;t change."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 420497.0,
      "end_time": 423554.0,
      "text": "And addressing these non-obvious core issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 423578.0,
      "end_time": 425387.0,
      "text": "became a key part of the program."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 426678.0,
      "end_time": 429630.0,
      "text": "So, we had the goal and we had the issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429654.0,
      "end_time": 432403.0,
      "text": "and now we needed to figure out what the solutions were."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 432888.0,
      "end_time": 435325.0,
      "text": "We obviously did not want to recreate the wheel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435350.0,
      "end_time": 438100.0,
      "text": "so we said, \"Let&#39;s look around and see what we can find.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438490.0,
      "end_time": 443387.0,
      "text": "And we found these beautiful, small pilot experiments"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 443411.0,
      "end_time": 445582.0,
      "text": "all over the country and all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 446146.0,
      "end_time": 450114.0,
      "text": "Small things being done by NGOs, being done by foundations."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 450138.0,
      "end_time": 454940.0,
      "text": "But what was also interesting was that none of them actually scaled."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 454119.0,
      "end_time": 457657.0,
      "text": "All of them were limited to 50, 100 or 500 schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 457681.0,
      "end_time": 460721.0,
      "text": "And here, we were looking for a solution for 15,000 schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 461180.0,
      "end_time": 462884.0,
      "text": "So we looked into why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 462908.0,
      "end_time": 466230.0,
      "text": "if these things actually work, why don&#39;t they actually scale?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 466572.0,
      "end_time": 469807.0,
      "text": "What happens is that when a typical NGO comes in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 469831.0,
      "end_time": 472244.0,
      "text": "they not only bring in their expertise"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 472268.0,
      "end_time": 474782.0,
      "text": "but they also bring in additional resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474807.0,
      "end_time": 476564.0,
      "text": "So they might bring in money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 476588.0,
      "end_time": 477909.0,
      "text": "they might bring in people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 477933.0,
      "end_time": 479627.0,
      "text": "they might bring in technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479651.0,
      "end_time": 484400.0,
      "text": "And in the 50 or 100 schools that they actually operate in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 484640.0,
      "end_time": 486924.0,
      "text": "those additional resources actually create a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 487476.0,
      "end_time": 490800.0,
      "text": "But now imagine that the head of this NGO"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 490320.0,
      "end_time": 492787.0,
      "text": "goes to the head of the School Education Department"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 492811.0,
      "end_time": 496750.0,
      "text": "and says, \"Hey, now let&#39;s do this for 15,000 schools.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 496100.0,
      "end_time": 499553.0,
      "text": "Where is that guy or girl going to find the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 499577.0,
      "end_time": 502281.0,
      "text": "to actually scale this up to 15,000 schools?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502305.0,
      "end_time": 504670.0,
      "text": "He doesn&#39;t have the additional money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 504910.0,
      "end_time": 505688.0,
      "text": "he doesn&#39;t have the resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 505712.0,
      "end_time": 508630.0,
      "text": "And hence, innovations don&#39;t scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 508938.0,
      "end_time": 512341.0,
      "text": "So right at the beginning of the project, what we said was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 512365.0,
      "end_time": 515100.0,
      "text": "\"Whatever we have to do has to be scalable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 515340.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518322.00000000006,
      "text": "it has to work in all 15,000 schools.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 518346.0,
      "end_time": 522138.0,
      "text": "And hence, it has to work within the existing budgets"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 522162.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524693.0,
      "text": "and resources that the state actually has."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 525552.0,
      "end_time": 527427.0,
      "text": "Much easier said than done."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 527451.0,
      "end_time": 528840.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528864.0,
      "end_time": 531200.0,
      "text": "I think this was definitely the point in time"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 531440.0,
      "end_time": 532888.0,
      "text": "when my team hated me."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 532912.0,
      "end_time": 538900.0,
      "text": "We spent a lot of long hours in office, in caf√©s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 538114.0,
      "end_time": 539409.0,
      "text": "sometimes even in bars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 539433.0,
      "end_time": 541960.0,
      "text": "scratching out heads and saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 541120.0,
      "end_time": 544386.0,
      "text": "\"Where are the solutions, how are we going to solve this problem?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 544410.0,
      "end_time": 548189.0,
      "text": "In the end, I think we did find solutions to many of the issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 548214.0,
      "end_time": 550870.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 550111.0,
      "end_time": 552530.0,
      "text": "In the context of effective learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 552770.0,
      "end_time": 555362.0,
      "text": "one of the things people talk about is hands-on learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 555386.0,
      "end_time": 557654.0,
      "text": "Children shouldn&#39;t memorize things from books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 557678.0,
      "end_time": 559267.0,
      "text": "they should do activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 559291.0,
      "end_time": 561290.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s a more effective way to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 561314.0,
      "end_time": 563612.0,
      "text": "Which basically means giving students things"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 563636.0,
      "end_time": 567580.0,
      "text": "like beads, learning rods, abacuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 567820.0,
      "end_time": 569536.0,
      "text": "But we did not have the budgets to give that"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 569560.0,
      "end_time": 572175.0,
      "text": "to 15,000 schools, 2 million children."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 572199.0,
      "end_time": 573901.0,
      "text": "We needed another solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 574446.0,
      "end_time": 575992.0,
      "text": "We couldn&#39;t think of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 576368.0,
      "end_time": 579197.0,
      "text": "One day, one of our team members went to a school"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 579221.0,
      "end_time": 583587.0,
      "text": "and saw a teacher pick up sticks and stones from the garden outside"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 583611.0,
      "end_time": 585432.0,
      "text": "and take them into the classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 585456.0,
      "end_time": 586968.0,
      "text": "and give them to the students."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 587726.0,
      "end_time": 590633.0,
      "text": "That was a huge eureka moment for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 591617.0,
      "end_time": 594500.0,
      "text": "So what happens now in the textbooks in Haryana"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 594524.0,
      "end_time": 597266.0,
      "text": "is that after every concept, we have a little box"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 597290.0,
      "end_time": 599678.0,
      "text": "which are instructions for the teachers which say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 599702.0,
      "end_time": 603858.0,
      "text": "\"To teach this concept, here&#39;s an activity that you can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 603882.0,
      "end_time": 606968.0,
      "text": "And by the way, in order to actually do this activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 606993.0,
      "end_time": 610172.0,
      "text": "here are things that you can use from your immediate environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 610196.0,
      "end_time": 613217.0,
      "text": "whether it be the garden outside or the classroom inside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 613241.0,
      "end_time": 615686.0,
      "text": "which can be used as learning aids for kids.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 616194.0,
      "end_time": 618640.0,
      "text": "And we see teachers all over Haryana"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 618664.0,
      "end_time": 621914.0,
      "text": "using lots of innovative things to be able to teach students."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 622617.0,
      "end_time": 626202.0,
      "text": "So in this way, whatever we designed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 626226.0,
      "end_time": 628304.0,
      "text": "we were actually able to implement it"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 628328.0,
      "end_time": 631132.0,
      "text": "across all 15,000 schools from day one."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 632304.0,
      "end_time": 634490.0,
      "text": "Now, this brings me to my last point."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 634514.0,
      "end_time": 637787.0,
      "text": "How do you implement something across 15,000 schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 637811.0,
      "end_time": 639568.0,
      "text": "and 100,000 teachers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 640357.0,
      "end_time": 642379.0,
      "text": "The department used to have a process"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 642403.0,
      "end_time": 643677.0,
      "text": "which is very interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 643701.0,
      "end_time": 646402.0,
      "text": "I like to call it \"The Chain of Hope.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 648240.0,
      "end_time": 650600.0,
      "text": "They would write a letter from the headquarters"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 650624.0,
      "end_time": 652249.0,
      "text": "and send it to the next level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 652273.0,
      "end_time": 653756.0,
      "text": "which was the district offices."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 654186.0,
      "end_time": 656843.0,
      "text": "They would hope that in each of these district offices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 656867.0,
      "end_time": 660842.0,
      "text": "an officer would get the letter, would open it, read it"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 660866.0,
      "end_time": 662960.0,
      "text": "and then forward it to the next level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 662984.0,
      "end_time": 664991.0,
      "text": "which was the block offices."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 665150.0,
      "end_time": 668780.0,
      "text": "And then you would hope that at the block office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 668804.0,
      "end_time": 670286.0,
      "text": "somebody else got the letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 670311.0,
      "end_time": 674330.0,
      "text": "opened it, read it and forwarded it eventually to the 15,000 principals."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 674354.0,
      "end_time": 677130.0,
      "text": "And then one would hope that the principals"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 677370.0,
      "end_time": 679684.0,
      "text": "got the letter, received it, understood it"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 679708.0,
      "end_time": 681637.0,
      "text": "and started implementing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 681662.0,
      "end_time": 683309.0,
      "text": "It was a little bit ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 684684.0,
      "end_time": 687145.0,
      "text": "Now, we knew technology was the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 687169.0,
      "end_time": 689310.0,
      "text": "but we also knew that most of these schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 689334.0,
      "end_time": 691411.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t have a computer or email."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 692497.0,
      "end_time": 695579.0,
      "text": "However, what the teachers do have are smartphones."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 695604.0,
      "end_time": 700283.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re constantly on SMS, on Facebook and on WhatsApp."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 700650.0,
      "end_time": 702895.0,
      "text": "So what now happens in Haryana is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 702919.0,
      "end_time": 707539.0,
      "text": "all principals and teachers are divided into hundreds of WhatsApp groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 707563.0,
      "end_time": 710385.0,
      "text": "and anytime something needs to be communicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 710409.0,
      "end_time": 712830.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just posted across all WhatsApp groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 713486.0,
      "end_time": 715687.0,
      "text": "It spreads like wildfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 715711.0,
      "end_time": 718704.0,
      "text": "You can immediately check who has received it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 718728.0,
      "end_time": 720170.0,
      "text": "who has read it."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 720420.0,
      "end_time": 723902.0,
      "text": "Teachers can ask clarification questions instantaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 723926.0,
      "end_time": 725167.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s interesting is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 725191.0,
      "end_time": 728549.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not just the headquarters who are answering these questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 728573.0,
      "end_time": 731462.0,
      "text": "Another teacher from a completely different part of the state"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 731486.0,
      "end_time": 733879.0,
      "text": "will stand up and answer the question."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 733903.0,
      "end_time": 736583.0,
      "text": "Everybody&#39;s acting as everybody&#39;s peer group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 736607.0,
      "end_time": 738401.0,
      "text": "and things are getting implemented."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 739784.0,
      "end_time": 742670.0,
      "text": "So today, when you go to a school in Haryana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 742910.0,
      "end_time": 743678.0,
      "text": "things look different."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 743702.0,
      "end_time": 746132.0,
      "text": "The teachers are back inside classrooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 746156.0,
      "end_time": 747459.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re teaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 747484.0,
      "end_time": 749342.0,
      "text": "Often with innovative techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 749740.0,
      "end_time": 752842.0,
      "text": "When a supervisor comes to visit the classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 752866.0,
      "end_time": 756733.0,
      "text": "he or she not only checks the construction of the toilet"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 756757.0,
      "end_time": 759990.0,
      "text": "but also what is the quality of teaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 760920.0,
      "end_time": 763208.0,
      "text": "Once a quarter, all students across the state"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 763232.0,
      "end_time": 765396.0,
      "text": "are assessed on their learning outcomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 765421.0,
      "end_time": 768279.0,
      "text": "and schools which are doing well are rewarded."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 768303.0,
      "end_time": 770772.0,
      "text": "And schools which are not doing so well"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 770796.0,
      "end_time": 773201.0,
      "text": "find themselves having difficult conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 773568.0,
      "end_time": 775646.0,
      "text": "Of course, they also get additional support"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 775671.0,
      "end_time": 777607.0,
      "text": "to be able to do better in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 779232.0,
      "end_time": 780856.0,
      "text": "In the context of education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 780880.0,
      "end_time": 783247.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very difficult to see results quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 783630.0,
      "end_time": 786605.0,
      "text": "When people talk about systemic, large-scale change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 786629.0,
      "end_time": 790208.0,
      "text": "they talk about periods of 7 years and 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 790232.0,
      "end_time": 791497.0,
      "text": "But not in Haryana."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 792153.0,
      "end_time": 796105.0,
      "text": "In the last one year, there have been three independent studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 796129.0,
      "end_time": 798708.0,
      "text": "all measuring student learning outcomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 798732.0,
      "end_time": 801390.0,
      "text": "which indicate that something fundamental,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 801630.0,
      "end_time": 803153.0,
      "text": "something unique is happening in Haryana."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 803622.0,
      "end_time": 806630.0,
      "text": "Learning levels of children have stopped declining,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 806654.0,
      "end_time": 808457.0,
      "text": "and they have started going up."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 808481.0,
      "end_time": 811691.0,
      "text": "Haryana is one of the few states in the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 811715.0,
      "end_time": 813294.0,
      "text": "which is showing an improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 813318.0,
      "end_time": 817210.0,
      "text": "and certainly the one that is showing the fastest rate of improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 818500.0,
      "end_time": 819373.0,
      "text": "These are still early signs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 819397.0,
      "end_time": 820591.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a long way to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 820615.0,
      "end_time": 823106.0,
      "text": "but this gives us a lot of hope for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 824859.0,
      "end_time": 826422.0,
      "text": "I recently went to a school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 826446.0,
      "end_time": 828389.0,
      "text": "and as I was leaving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 828413.0,
      "end_time": 829564.0,
      "text": "I ran into a lady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 829588.0,
      "end_time": 830738.0,
      "text": "her name was Parvati,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 830763.0,
      "end_time": 832201.0,
      "text": "she was the mother of a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 832225.0,
      "end_time": 833496.0,
      "text": "and she was smiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 833828.0,
      "end_time": 836737.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Why are you smiling, what&#39;s going on?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 836761.0,
      "end_time": 839507.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"I don&#39;t know what&#39;s going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 839531.0,
      "end_time": 842617.0,
      "text": "but what I do know is that my children are learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 842642.0,
      "end_time": 844930.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re having fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 844117.0,
      "end_time": 847312.0,
      "text": "and for the time being, I&#39;ll stop my search for a private school"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 847336.0,
      "end_time": 848499.0,
      "text": "to send them to.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 849523.0,
      "end_time": 851523.0,
      "text": "So I go back to where I started:"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 851547.0,
      "end_time": 853421.0,
      "text": "Can government systems transform?"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 854163.0,
      "end_time": 855663.0,
      "text": "I certainly believe so."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 855687.0,
      "end_time": 857781.0,
      "text": "I think if you give them the right levers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 857805.0,
      "end_time": 859287.0,
      "text": "they can move mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 859735.0,
      "end_time": 860886.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 860910.0,
      "end_time": 867250.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}